.SS "void Deck::shuffle ()"

.PP
Randomly shuffles the order of cards in the deck\&. Uses a Mersenne Twister pseudo-random generator seeded from std::random_device\&. Suitable for gameplay randomness but not cryptographically secure\&.

.PP
\fBPostcondition\fP
.RS 4
All cards remain present, but in randomized order\&.
.RE
.PP
Uses std::shuffle with Mersenne Twister (mt19937) seeded from random_device\&. Ensures fair shuffling each time it’s called\&. 
